row-af89101&quot;,&quot;rtl&quot;:false}' dir=\"ltr\"><div class=\"jet-testimonials__item\">\n\t<div class=\"jet-testimonials__item-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"jet-testimonials__content\"><h5 class=\"jet-testimonials__title\">Priya N., India<\/h5><div class=\"jet-testimonials__comment\">We loved how Pumo Tours and Safaris combined authentic cultural experiences with high-end comfort. Whether we were tracking gorillas or enjoying a sunset dinner, every moment felt meaningful and magical. This was more than a trip..<\/div><div class=\"jet-testimonials__name\"><span>Mark & Elena P., Australia<\/span><\/div><div class=\"jet-testimonials__rating\" data-rating=\"5\"><i aria-hidden=\"true\" data-star=\"fas fa-star\" data-active-star=\"fas fa-star\"><\/i><i aria-hidden=\"true\" data-star=\"fas fa-star\" data-active-star=\"fas fa-star\"><\/i><i aria-hidden=\"true\" data-star=\"fas fa-star\" data-active-star=\"fas fa-star\"><\/i><i aria-hidden=\"true\" data-star=\"fas fa-star\" data-active-star=\"fas fa-star\"><\/i><i aria-hidden=\"true\" data-star=\"fas fa-star\" data-active-star=\"fas fa-star\"><\/i><\/div><\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"jet-testimonials__item\">\n\t<div class=\"jet-testimonials__item-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"jet-testimonials__content\"><h5 class=\"jet-testimonials__title\">Beyond Expectations<\/h5><div class=\"jet-testimonials__comment\">We wanted something unique and thrilling \u2014 and Pumo Tours and Safaris overdelivered. From the breathtaking views of the Rift Valley to personalized service throughout, everything felt tailored just for us. We\u2019ve traveled a lot, but this was truly next-level.<\/div><div class=\"jet-testimonials__name\"><span>Leila K., United Kingdom<\/span><\/div><div class=\"jet-testimonials__rating\" data-rating=\"5\"><i aria-hidden=\"true\" data-star=\"fas fa-star\" data-active-star=\"fas fa-star\"><\/i><i aria-hidden=\"true\" data-star=\"fas fa-star\" data-active-star=\"fas fa-star\"><\/i><i aria-hidden=\"true\" data-star=\"fas fa-star\" data-active-star=\"fas fa-star\"><\/i><i aria-hidden=\"true\" data-star=\"fas fa-star\" data-active-star=\"fas fa-star\"><\/i><i aria-hidden=\"true\" data-star=\"fas fa-star\" data-active-star=\"fas fa-star\"><\/i><\/div><\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"jet-testimonials__item\">\n\t<div class=\"jet-testimonials__item-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"jet-testimonials__content\"><h5 class=\"jet-testimonials__title\">First-Class From Start to Finish<\/h5><div class=\"jet-testimonials__comment\">Booking with Pumo Tours and Safaris  was seamless, and the experience was flawless. Our private guide was exceptional, the accommodations were world-class, and the itinerary was thrilling yet relaxed. It\u2019s rare to find such luxury in adventure travel.<\/div><div class=\"jet-testimonials__name\"><span>Mark & Elena P., Australia<\/span><\/div><div class=\"jet-testimonials__rating\" data-rating=\"5\"><i aria-hidden=\"true\" data-star=\"fas fa-star\" data-active-star=\"fas fa-star\"><\/i><i aria-hidden=\"true\" data-star=\"fas fa-star\" data-active-star=\"fas fa-star\"><\/i><i aria-hidden=\"true\" data-star=\"fas fa-star\" data-active-star=\"fas fa-star\"><\/i><i aria-hidden=\"true\" data-star=\"fas fa-star\" data-active-star=\"fas fa-star\"><\/i><i aria-hidden=\"true\" data-star=\"fas fa-star\" data-active-star=\"fas fa-star\"><\/i><\/div><\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"jet-testimonials__item\">\n\t<div class=\"jet-testimonials__item-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"jet-testimonials__content\"><h5 class=\"jet-testimonials__title\">An Unforgettable Luxury Safari<\/h5><div class=\"jet-testimonials__comment\">Pumo Tours and Safaris  delivered the perfect balance of adventure and comfort. Every detail was handled with care, from our guide\u2019s knowledge to the stunning lodges. Seeing the Big Five up close while staying in pure luxury made this a trip of a lifetime.<\/div><div class=\"jet-testimonials__name\"><span>S